cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DC, cs.CR, cs.SI

The paper discusses techniques for personalizing machine learning models in the context of federated learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The paper also discusses privacy concerns, which could place it in the cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) category. Finally, the paper discusses the statistical heterogeneity of data across devices, which could place it in the cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) category.
